713235f.title: Manhattan: 45th Street (West) - 10th Avenue
713235f.text:
West 45th Street, west from Tenth Avenue, showing progress
of the W. P. A. repaving program on this thoroughfare.
View 2 is photographed from a point closer to Eleventh Ave.
June 17, 1937
No's. 1-2
W. P. A., photo
Five Boroughs Project
CREDIT LINE IMPERATIVE
